ed="T" n="0817c06"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0817c06"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011456"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>千頃山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A003631">楚南</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0817c07"/><persName key="A003631">釋楚南</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000017166">閩</placeName>人也，俗姓<name>張</name>氏。爰在髫齡，冥然<lb
ed="T" n="0817c08"/>跪於父母前，訴志出家。投<placeName key="PL000000017126">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A011941">曇藹<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0817c09"/>而受訓焉。當授經法，目所經覩，輒誦於<lb
ed="T" n="0817c10"/>口。執巾侍盥，灑掃應對，頗能謹愿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1134"/>。迨乎<date key="j20249822025335" from-iso="+0832-02-10" to-iso="+0833-01-28">冠<lb
ed="T" n="0817c11"/>歲</date>，乃落髮焉。詣<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>登戒，就<placeName key="PL000000001058">趙郡</placeName>學<placeName key="PL000000024082">相<lb
ed="T" n="0817c12"/>部</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>律<ptr target="#n911"/>。往<placeName key="PL000000042189">上都</placeName>，學《淨名經》。一律一經，略通宗<lb
ed="T" n="0817c13"/>旨，則知頓機，不甘為漸教縛。遂往<placeName key="PL000000057110">芙蓉<lb
ed="T" n="0817c14"/>山</placeName>，根性未發<ptr target="#n502"/>。謁<persName key="A000490">黃蘗山<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，問答雖多，機<lb
ed="T" n="0817c15"/>宜頓了。倏值<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>廢教，<persName key="A003631">南</persName>遂深竄林谷。<date from-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大<lb
ed="T" n="0817c16"/>中</name></date>興教，出遇昇平相<persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>公</roleName>休</persName>出撫<placeName key="PL000000016956">宛陵</placeName><ptr target="#n2256"/>，請<lb
ed="T" n="0817c17"/><persName key="A000490">黃蘗</persName>出山，<persName key="A003631">南</persName>隨侍。由此便詣<placeName key="PL000000009882"><placeName>姑蘇</placeName><placeName>報恩寺</placeName></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0817c18"/>專行禪定，足不踰閾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g641"/>，僅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g175"/>二十餘載。<date from-iso="+0877-01-22" key="j20414002041783" to-iso="+0878-02-09"><name>乾符</name>四<lb
ed="T" n="0817c19"/>年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000009928">蘇州</placeName>太守<persName key="A011945">周慎嗣</persName>嚮風，請住<placeName key="PL000000010087">寶林院</placeName>。又請<lb
ed="T" n="0817c20"/>居<placeName key="PL000000010025">支硎山</placeName>。至<date from-iso="+0878-02-10" key="j20417842042137" to-iso="+0879-01-29">五年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000012138">昌化縣</placeName>令<persName key="A011949">徐正元</persName>與<placeName key="PL000000012144">紫<lb
ed="T" n="0817c21"/>溪</placeName>戍將<persName key="A011950">饒京</persName>同召住<placeName key="PL000000011466"><placeName>千頃</placeName><placeName>慈雲院</placeName></placeName>。訓示禪<lb
ed="T" n="0817c22"/>徒之外，唯儼然在定，逾月或浹旬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g287"/>。<date from-iso="+0887-02-01" key="j20450622045445" to-iso="+0888-02-19"><name>光啟</name>三<lb
ed="T" n="0817c23"/>年</date>，前<placeName key="PL000000008355">兩浙</placeName><persName key="A003552"><persName>武肅王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>請下山供施。<persName key="A003875">昭宗</persName>聞<lb
ed="T" n="0817c24"/>其道化，賜其鹿胎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1137"/>衣五事，別齎紫衣。<date from-iso="+0888-03-21" key="j20454762045504" to-iso="+0888-04-18"><name>文德</name><lb
ed="T" n="0817c25"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>六</sic><corr>元</corr></choice>年二月</date><ptr target="#n2226"/>，忽雙虹貫堂室，二鹿蹶然入寺，法<lb
ed="T" n="0817c26"/>堂梁折。至<date from-iso="+0888-06-17" key="j20455642045593" to-iso="+0888-07-16">五月</date>，辭眾，後於禪床垂兩足、伸<lb
ed="T" n="0817c27"/>二臂于膝，奄然而卒。春秋七十<ptr target="#n2227"/>，僧臘五十六。<lb
ed="T" n="0817c28"/>遷塔于院西隅。<date from-iso="+0892-03-07" key="j20469232046951" to-iso="+0892-04-04"><name>大順</name><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>二</sic><corr>三</corr></choice>年壬子歲二月</date><ptr target="#n2228"/>，<placeName key="PL000000016955">宣州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0817c29"/><persName key="A009841">孫儒</persName>寇<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢唐</placeName>之封略<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1151"/>。兵士發塔，見<persName key="A003631">南</persName>全身不<pb ed="T" n="0818a" xml:id="T50.2061.0818a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0818a01"/>散，爪髮俱長，悔罪而去。<persName key="A003631">南<roleName>公</roleName></persName>平昔著《般若<lb
ed="T" n="0818a02"/>經品頌偈》一卷、《破邪論》一卷，以枝梧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1398"/>異宗外<lb
ed="T" n="0818a03"/>敵，見貴於時也。</p>
